summary: Stuff for a project that I'm working on at school. Anime intro for Past of your Present. The project was to create an intro of...
body: Stuff for a project that I’m working on at school. Anime intro for Past of your Present. The project was to create an intro of something(like an intro to a movie or show) and I went with an anime intro because I’ve got too much confidence and imagination when it come to this kinda stuff. I over think it and put too much work into it when I really shouldn’t but eeeeehhhh ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
